{"uuid":"fd98b22d-0a16-46d4-ab1e-53170288e1d4","createDate":1714628763610,"customConfigJson":"{name: \"First Steps for Quest 2\", link: \"https://www.meta.com/zh-tw/experiences/first-steps-for-quest-2/3675568169182204/\"}","type":"quest3Review","title":"评测 > First Steps for Quest 2（初次接触）","content":"<div style=\"direction: ltr; border-width: 100%;\">\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; margin-top: 0in; margin-left: 0in; width: 7.6041in;\">\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; margin-top: 0in; margin-left: 0in; width: 7.6041in;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\">这是在</span><span lang=\"en-US\">Meta Quest 3</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\">自带的免费小游戏，建议每个玩家的第一个游戏就玩这个。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">游戏流程很短，几分钟的小游戏。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">游戏名称中文名叫初次接触，商店页面叫First Steps for Quest 2想来是兼容老设备的游戏。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">进入游戏后首先要扫描当前房间场景，然后确定移动范围。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">最后就能开始游戏了。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">这是个捕捉毛绒怪的小游戏，游戏场景会显示之前扫描的房间。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">开场房间某个天花板碎开，从里面降落下外星飞船，玩家从飞船中获取扫描枪来扫描房间墙面能看到房间外的场景。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">这时候就会出现毛绒怪在外面砸墙，慢慢就会出现毛绒怪跑到房间里的情况。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">之前的扫描枪这下就变成捕获枪，可以突突突并将毛绒怪捕获到飞船上。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">开始倒计时，倒计时前尽可能捕获更多的毛绒怪。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">突突突的过程中会把墙壁砸坏，并看到外面的外星场景，体验很棒。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">最后倒计时结束，毛绒怪全部被收集到飞船上，并乘坐飞船离开。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">并显示玩家分数。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 11.0pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\">算是</span><span lang=\"en-US\">Quest3</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\">中的基础小游戏了。</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","bgArchivesType":{"uuid":"0ccea8dd-ea64-4f19-9573-4d5bad74ab84","code":"Quest游戏评测","name":"Quest游戏评测","parentUuid":"a4fb2b94-3d2b-414d-8745-49677c3c7d22"}}